## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open `FinTrack_Pipeline.ipynb` in Google Colab
2. Run all cells in order
3. The pipeline will automatically:
   - Pull customer data from API
   - Generate 500 realistic transactions
   - Validate every row with Pydantic
   - Clean and store in `fintrack.db`
   - Answer all 6 business questions
   - Generate 4 visualizations

